{"tid":293030,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"用carosell賣野隨時比班ON9仔D問題激撚死","createTime":"2017-06-21T23:42:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-23T10:57:00.000Z","uid":8129,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"544d4f0f4760ff7c2ee60fb89693ae65814c54e3","tid":293030,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T23:42:22.000Z","msg":"不解釋"},{"pid":"903266e21c6215e55937a49c682de9aa85ac999b","tid":293030,"uid":8129,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T23:49:12.000Z","msg":"有一堆ON9仔一味問唔會買不在話下。<br />\n<br />\n有條撚屌，都講到明全新，張圖又影撚住個盒，仲問我有冇盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又問可唔可以影多幾張黎睇，盒都已經POST左前後兩張，仲可以將個盒影D乜撚野比你睇呀? 影埋上下? 屌你老母睇個盒把撚咩? 你買件貨定買個盒? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有件八婆約好晒時間，地點，最後問下佢住邊，原來同佢住隔一個區，諗住好心就下佢唔駛約咁遠就問佢不如係佢個區某地方等，個度就近佢區多D，我就剩係去都要行十幾廿分鐘，屌你老母佢同我講話可唔可以係另一度等，話都係差唔多，個個位離我仲遠，比我提出原定位置要行多兩三條街，一來一回我都要九個字，即係要我搭車去佢附近，我話好遠，話不如照返原定個地點，之後唔應機潛水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有件阿嬸仲撚ON9，一件野賣幾十蚊，又影相又盛又約時間，全部有共識OK後到最後問我，可唔可以平十蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我賣既野唔多，但已經成日遇到呢D ON9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8170919cac71c6a7a91064480fb36b2a3c37b19e","tid":293030,"uid":26115,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T23:52:53.000Z","msg":"最ON9係問 你會唔會呃我 果D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係呃你果D會唔會話自己呃你，D ON9仔唔撚用腦問埋哂D ON9問題，見親都眼火爆即刻串鳩D傻閪會呀我係騙子呀"},{"pid":"2fd560847b5146538c12b45547c4bedb4f38820f","tid":293030,"uid":8129,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T09:28:55.000Z","msg":"carosell on9仔負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3900333fec6474aaf857347e95baaafd988d88d","tid":293030,"uid":66779,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T09:51:29.000Z","msg":"用過 似係公司請返嚟專問嘢 等真用家以為個app多人用 繼而繼續用 識人做緊類似嘢 一個月一千報酬到 carousell應該少啲"},{"pid":"c78f358cda0998b10bfcddcc79cf7f982606bdb2","tid":293030,"uid":103921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T09:54:49.000Z","msg":"其實全部賣野平台都好多戇鳩仔。<br />\n最中意左問右問又唔係買，一係排膠價。"},{"pid":"83a2b962bd5c95aedd9b7def3fcce71fa038e181","tid":293030,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T09:59:30.000Z","msg":"睇下幾時變Yahoo知識+翻版,成版都係膠問膠答 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />lm"},{"pid":"8a1e67a17ced24997203750889b90b4c3aed9621","tid":293030,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T11:59:30.000Z","msg":"carosell<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28863edd8c63f94034707830763678ae76f7784c","tid":293030,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T07:02:45.000Z","msg":"肥花一樣多r價乞衣<br />\n試過俾人打電話r到面交<br />\n一蚊都唔減畀佢"},{"pid":"01ac34b2e6c45b67361b354302e66f14db60daef","tid":293030,"uid":342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T07:03:59.000Z","msg":"carousell呀戇鳩"},{"pid":"87834dbe12e6033e2ae97ff3f4c528e8bcf47fac","tid":293030,"uid":8129,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T10:43:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>carousell呀戇鳩</blockquote><br />\n威 型 帥"},{"pid":"5dd4dec4313b82d5f12354c5e0809cb480dcb14f","tid":293030,"uid":43308,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T10:52:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ba39363356fbcd49b91510d9cd339b56a22ac0d2","tid":293030,"uid":25845,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T10:57:00.000Z","msg":"啲人眼殘唔識睇字, 垃圾"}]}